title: Wild Card Weekend preview
itunes:title: Wild Card Weekend preview
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game previewing each Wild Card matchup as the playoffs officially kick off this weekend. Plus, Conor Orr joins from his New Jersey Haunted Mansion with a special announcement.
